          <div class="pc-card-img" style="background-image:url('https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/5027-1.jpg')" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="pc-card-body">
            <span class="pc-outlet" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name">The Guardian</span></span>
            <h3 class="pc-card-title" itemprop="headline">Damning report published into death of baby born to teenager in prison cell</h3>
            <p class="pc-card-desc">Inquiry into how 18-year-old gave birth on her own in HMP Bronzefield in Ashford finds many failings</p>
            <div class="pc-card-footer">
              <time class="pc-date" datetime="2021-09-22" itemprop="datePublished">September 22, 2021</time>
              <span class="pc-tag" style="--tag-color:#CCFF33">Pregnancy in Prison</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2021/sep/22/damning-report-published-into-death-of-baby-born-to-teenager-in-prison-cell" />
        </a>
      </article>
      <article class="pc-card" data-topic="pregnancy-in-prison" aria-label="Pregnant woman’s jail sentence quashed in ‘landmark’ UK ruling" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
        <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2024/jan/19/pregnant-woman-jail-sentence-quashed-in-landmark-uk-ruling" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="pc-card-link">
          <div class="pc-card-img" style="background-image:url('https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/3500-2.jpg')" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></div>
